com.tibbo.aggregate.common.datatable

Class TableFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tibbo.aggregate.common.datatable.TableFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PublicCloneable, StringEncodable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<FieldFormat>

    public class TableFormat
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<FieldFormat>, java.lang.Cloneable, PublicCloneable, StringEncodable
    TableFormat describes fields and other options of a DataTable or a DataRecord.
